description: Police are accused of using brutal tactics at another Sunday rally against President Lukashenko.
title: Belarus: Dozens arrested as police blast protesters with water cannon
title_page: Belarus: Dozens arrested as police blast protesters with water cannon - BBC News
maintext: A short video clip shared by the press service also shows Mr Lukashenko saying to the group: "I am trying to convince not only your supporters but the whole of society that we need to look at things more broadly."
